PrecisOrder (a) accepting a retrocession from the COMMISSIONER of the NORTHWEST TERRITORIES of some 145,000 hectares of land situate on the Meta Incognita Peninsula of BAFFIN ISLAND, and (b) retransferring them to the Commissioner for the establishment of KATANNILIK TERRITORIAL PARK, saving and excepting thereout and therefrom all mines and minerals, the beds of bodies of water and the riparian rights connected therewith.
